
<head>
  <title><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> – Payments & Quotes</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <style>
    /* ========= <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> Payments Page ========= */

    .pay-page {
      --bg: #f5f5fb;
      --bg-card: #ffffff;
      --text-main: #111827;
      --text-sub: #4b5563;
      --muted: #6b7280;
      --border-soft: #e5e7eb;
      --accent: #4f46e5;
      --accent-soft: #eef2ff;
      --accent-dark: #312e81;
      --accent-green: #16a34a;
      --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      --radius-lg: 18px;
      --radius-md: 14px;
      --radius-pill: 999px;

      font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      color: var(--text-main);
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #eef2ff 0, #f9fafb 40%, #f3f4f6 100%);
      padding: 40px 16px 72px;
    }

    .pay-page * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    .pay-shell {
      max-width: 1120px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    /* ---------- Hero ---------- */

    .pay-hero {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-top: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .pay-hero {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .pay-kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #ffffff, #eef2ff);
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.09em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .pay-kicker-dot {
      width: 8px;
      height: 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #a5b4fc 0, #4f46e5 55%, #1e1b4b 100%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.9);
    }

    .pay-title {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 4.2vw, 40px);
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.035em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .pay-title span {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .pay-sub {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 520px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .pay-hero-note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .pay-cta-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .btn-pill {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: transform 0.12s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease, background 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
      border-color: rgba(191, 219, 254, 0.9);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 18px 38px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #ffffff;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.6);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #f3f4ff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    .pay-hero-foot {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .pay-hero-foot span {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .pay-hero-media {
      position: relative;
    }

    .pay-hero-card {
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.25), rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98));
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .pay-hero-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .pay-hero-chip {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.5);
    }

    .pay-hero-status {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.18);
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.7);
      color: #bbf7d0;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .pay-hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      margin-top: 6px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .pay-hero-stat label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 10px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .pay-hero-stat strong {
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .pay-hero-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .pay-hero-meta code {
      font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, "Liberation Mono",
        "Courier New", monospace;
      font-size: 11px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.85);
      padding: 2px 5px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      color: #e0e7ff;
    }

    .pay-hero-footer {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 10px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .pay-hero-footer span {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .pay-hero-footer-dot {
      width: 6px;
      height: 6px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #22c55e;
      box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.9);
    }

    .pay-hero-shadow {
      position: absolute;
      inset: 18px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    /* ---------- Intro ---------- */

    .pay-intro {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .pay-intro h2 {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .pay-intro p {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .pay-intro strong {
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ---------- Feature grid (top-level) ---------- */

    .pay-feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
      margin-bottom: 56px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .pay-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .pay-feature-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .pay-feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
      padding: 18px 18px 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 8px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .pay-feature-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 2px;
    }

    .pay-feature-title {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .pay-feature-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .pay-feature-meta {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ---------- Two-column sections ---------- */

    .pay-section-block {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 36px;
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
    }

    .pay-section-block.reverse {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.2fr);
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .pay-section-block,
      .pay-section-block.reverse {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .pay-section-label {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .pay-section-title {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .pay-section-text {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .pay-section-text + .pay-section-text {
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .pay-section-list {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      padding-left: 18px;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .pay-section-list li {
      margin-bottom: 3px;
    }

    .pay-section-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.06);
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .pay-section-card h3 {
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .pay-section-card p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .pay-pill-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .pay-pill {
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      font-size: 11px;
      background: var(--accent-soft);
      color: var(--accent-dark);
    }

    .pay-pill.alt {
      background: #ecfdf5;
      color: #166534;
    }

    /* ---------- Section headings ---------- */

    .pay-section-heading {
      margin: 40px 0 16px;
    }

    .pay-section-kicker {
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .pay-section-main-title {
      font-size: 22px;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
    }

    .pay-section-sub {
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--text-sub);
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    /* ---------- Testimonials ---------- */

    .pay-testimonial-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0 52px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .pay-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .pay-testimonial-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .pay-testimonial-card {
      background: #0b1020;
      border-radius: var(--radius-md);
      padding: 18px 18px 16px;
      color: #e5e7eb;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6);
    }

    .pay-testimonial-card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5), transparent 55%);
      opacity: 0.9;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .pay-testimonial-logo {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.14em;
      color: #9ca3af;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .pay-testimonial-heading {
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 6px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .pay-testimonial-text {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #cbd5f5;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .pay-testimonial-person {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #9ca3af;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .pay-testimonial-person strong {
      display: block;
      color: #e5e7eb;
    }

    /* ---------- Articles ---------- */

    .pay-articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 24px 0 40px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .pay-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .pay-articles-grid {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .pay-article-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border-radius: 14px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border-soft);
      padding: 14px 14px 16px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.04);
    }

    .pay-article-tag {
      font-size: 11px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.16em;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .pay-article-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .pay-article-text {
      color: var(--text-sub);
    }

    .pay-article-meta {
      font-size: 11px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .pay-article-link {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: var(--accent-dark);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 4px;
    }

    .pay-article-link:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ---------- Newsletter ---------- */

    .pay-newsletter {
      margin-top: 16px;
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #111827, #020617);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.2fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    @media (max-width: 720px) {
      .pay-newsletter {
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr);
      }
    }

    .pay-newsletter h3 {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .pay-newsletter p {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #9ca3af;
    }

    .pay-newsletter-form {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 8px;
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }

    .pay-newsletter-input {
      flex: 1 1 180px;
      min-width: 0;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.7);
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      color: #e5e7eb;
      outline: none;
    }

    .pay-newsletter-input::placeholder {
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    .pay-newsletter-btn {
      padding: 8px 16px;
      border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
      border: none;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--accent), #6366f1);
      color: #f9fafb;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 500;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.5);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .pay-newsletter-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<%= render partial: "layouts/header" %>
<div class="pay-page" id="payments">
  <div class="pay-shell">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="pay-hero">
      <div>
        <h1 class="pay-title">
          Make it easy for customers to pay—<span>no chasing, no stress.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="pay-sub">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> connects quoting, invoicing and payments so you can move from first enquiry to paid
          job in just a few clicks. Customers pay the way they prefer, and your accounts stay up to date
          automatically.
        </p>
        <p class="pay-hero-note">
          Invite customers to set up automated payment methods, take card payments on-site, or let them
          pay securely online. However they pay, it’s all tracked back to the same customer record.
        </p>

        <div class="pay-cta-row">
          <a href="/users/sign_up" class="btn-pill btn-primary">Start a free trial</a>
          <a href="/pricing" class="btn-pill btn-secondary">See pricing</a>
        </div>
        <p class="pay-hero-foot">
          <span>Built-in tools for quotes, invoices and payments.</span> No extra systems to bolt on.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: payments mockup -->
      <div class="pay-hero-media">
        <div class="pay-hero-card">
          <div class="pay-hero-header">
            <div class="pay-hero-chip"><%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> · Payments</div>
            <div class="pay-hero-status">Invoice paid</div>
          </div>

          <div class="pay-hero-stats">
            <div class="pay-hero-stat">
              <label>Outstanding</label>
              <strong>$0.00</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="pay-hero-stat">
              <label>Paid this week</label>
              <strong>$8.4k</strong>
            </div>
            <div class="pay-hero-stat">
              <label>Auto-pay</label>
              <strong>74%</strong>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pay-hero-meta">
            Method: <code>Auto payment · Card · Stripe</code>
          </div>

          <div class="pay-hero-footer">
            <span>
              <span class="pay-hero-footer-dot"></span>
              Job → Invoice → Payment → Receipt
            </span>
            <span>Fully tracked in <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pay-hero-shadow"></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INTRO -->
    <section class="pay-intro">
      <h2>Streamline payments and quoting from one place.</h2>
      <p>
        Getting paid shouldn’t be the hardest part of the job. With <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %>, quoting, invoicing and
        payments all live in the same system, connected to your customers and your schedule.
      </p>
      <p>
        Create a quote, send it instantly, get notified when it’s approved and convert it to a job in
        a couple of clicks. Once the job is done, invoices can be sent automatically and paid online,
        in person, or via automated methods.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>Less chasing, fewer spreadsheets and clearer cash flow</strong> – so you can focus on
        doing great work, not tracking who still owes what.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- TOP-LEVEL FEATURE GRID -->
    <section class="pay-feature-grid">
      <article class="pay-feature-card">
        <p class="pay-feature-label">Automatic Payments</p>
        <h3 class="pay-feature-title">Let payments run in the background</h3>
        <p class="pay-feature-text">
          Invite customers to save a card on file or set up direct debit. When you mark the job complete,
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> triggers payment automatically and issues a receipt.
        </p>
        <p class="pay-feature-meta">
          Works with providers like Stripe and GoCardless so you don’t have to reinvent your payment stack.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="pay-feature-card">
        <p class="pay-feature-label">Manual &amp; Recorded Payments</p>
        <h3 class="pay-feature-title">Log payments in a couple of taps</h3>
        <p class="pay-feature-text">
          Cash, bank transfer or on-site card payment – however the customer pays, you can record it
          quickly and keep the invoice, customer and account balances in sync.
        </p>
        <p class="pay-feature-meta">
          No more paper notes or guessing what was paid where.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="pay-feature-card">
        <p class="pay-feature-label">Quotes &amp; Statements</p>
        <h3 class="pay-feature-title">From quote to statement, fully connected</h3>
        <p class="pay-feature-text">
          Generate professional quotes, convert them to jobs without retyping, and send clear customer
          statements that show every job, invoice and payment.
        </p>
        <p class="pay-feature-meta">
          Help customers see exactly what they owe and why.
        </p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <!-- DEEPER SECTIONS -->

    <!-- Automatic Payments -->
    <section class="pay-section-block">
      <div>
        <p class="pay-section-label">Automatic Payments</p>
        <h2 class="pay-section-title">Get paid automatically when jobs are complete.</h2>
        <p class="pay-section-text">
          <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> lets you offer automated payment options so customers are charged only once the job
          is marked as done. Set up recurring card payments through Stripe, or direct debit via providers
          like GoCardless.
        </p>
        <p class="pay-section-text">
          As soon as work is completed, <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> can send the invoice by SMS and email, trigger the
          payment request and send the customer a receipt – without you lifting a finger.
        </p>
        <ul class="pay-section-list">
          <li>Card-on-file and direct debit options</li>
          <li>Charge only when the job is complete</li>
          <li>Automatic receipts and notifications</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <aside class="pay-section-card">
        <div class="pay-pill-row">
          <span class="pay-pill">Stripe</span>
          <span class="pay-pill">GoCardless</span>
          <span class="pay-pill alt">Auto-pay</span>
        </div>
        <h3>Fewer late payments, better cash flow</h3>
        <p>
          With customers on automated payments, you can forecast income more accurately and spend far
          less time chasing outstanding invoices.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </section>

    <!-- Record Payments -->
    <section class="pay-section-block reverse">
      <aside class="pay-section-card">
        <div class="pay-pill-row">
          <span class="pay-pill">Cash &amp; Bank</span>
          <span class="pay-pill alt">Instant logging</span>
        </div>
        <h3>One place to record every payment</h3>
        <p>
          Whether it’s cash on the doorstep, a bank transfer that lands overnight or an online payment
          from a portal, logging it in <%= ENV['WEBSITE_NAME'] %> takes seconds.
        </p>
      </aside>

      <div>
        <p class="pay-section-label">Record Payments</p>
        <h2 class="pay-section-title">Log payments quickly and keep records accurate.</h2>
        <p class="pay-section-text">
